<i>noun</i>: 머리띠 [머리띠] <br>
<ul>
<li><i>noun</i><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>머리띠 [머리띠]</dt><br>
<dd>1. headband</dd><br>
<dd>이마에 두르는 띠.</dd><br>
<dd>A band that is worn around the forehead.</dd><br>
<dd>2. headband</dd><br>
<dd>액세서리의 하나로 머리를 고정시키는 둥근 모양의 띠.</dd><br>
<dd>A round-shaped band for fixing hair; a type of hair accessory.</dd><br>
</li>
</ul>